<plot>Based upon Harlan Ellison's classic short story, this CD-ROM adventure stars an omnipotent supercomputer calling itself AM as in "I think, therefore I am."). Built by the Americans as the ultimate defense system, AM accidentally became self-aware and eventually goes insane. Linking up with its Chinese and Russian counterparts, AM destroys the entire human race except for five people: Gorrister, the suicidal loner; Benny, the deformed war veteran; Ellen, the hysterical phobic; Nimdok, the secretive sadist; and Ted, the cynical paranoid. These damned souls have been kept alive and psychologically tortured for 105 years until AM begins a new game of metaphorical adventures based on each captive's fatal personality flaw.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?252446</url></doc>
